k <- NA
for(i in 1:10000){
    CNT <- 100
    x <- runif(CNT,min = -1,max = 1)
    y <- runif(CNT,min = -1,max = 1)
    a <- sum((x^2 + y^2) < 1)
    b <- CNT
    pi = 4*a/b
    k[i] = pi
}
hist(k,prob=T,col="light blue")

showPiList <- function(cnt){
    k <- NA
    for(i in 1:cnt){
        CNT <- 100
        x <- runif(CNT,min = -1,max = 1)
        y <- runif(CNT,min = -1,max = 1)
        a <- sum((x^2 + y^2) < 1)
        b <- CNT
        pi = 4*a/b
        k[i] = pi
    }
    k
}
showPiList(10000)

# rm(XL) 删除某个变量
x <- c(1,2,3,4,5,6,7)
XL <- function(y){
    mx <- mean(y)
    for(i in c(1:length(y))){
        if(y[i] > mx){
            y[i] <- y[i]/2
        } else if(y[i] < mx){
            y[i] <- y[i] * 2
        } else{
            y[i] <- y[i]*1.5
        }
    }
    print(y)
}
XL(x)

showPiLines <- function(cnt){
    k <- NA
    for(i in 1:cnt){
        CNT <- 100
        x <- runif(CNT,min = -1,max = 1)
        y <- runif(CNT,min = -1,max = 1)
        a <- sum((x^2 + y^2) < 1)
        b <- CNT
        pi = 4*a/b
        k[i] = pi
    }
}
p <- NA
for(i in 1:10000){
    if(k[i] > 3.1415){
        p[i] = k[i] - 3.1415
    } else if(k[i] < 3.1415){
        p[i] = k[i] - 3.1415
    } else{
        p[i] = k[i] - 3.1415
    }
}

#
model1 <- function(a,data){
    a[1] + data$x * a[2]
}

measure_distance <- function(mod, data) {
 diff <- data$y - model1(mod, data)
 sqrt(mean(diff ^ 2))
}

dist <- NA
CNT = 25000
# set.seed(250)
a1 = runif(CNT,-20,40)
a2 = runif(CNT,-5,5)
for(i in 1:CNT){
  dist[i] <- measure_distance(c(a1[i], a2[i]), sim1)
}

tb <- tibble(
      a1,a2,dist
    )

ggplot(sim1, aes(x, y)) +
geom_point(size = 2, color = "grey30") +
geom_abline(
aes(intercept = a1, slope = a2, color = -dist),
 data = filter(tb, rank(dist) <= 10)
 )
